Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.64,utaware def,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd use such\Na tactic in cold blood like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか平然と このような策を使うとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.48,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Brother!
